title: Brian Klaas on the 2016 US Presidential Election and Implications of a Trump Presidency
itunes:author: Brian Klaas
description: Contributor(s): Brian Klaas | As the world continues to digest the outcome of the 2016 US Presidential Election, Brian Klaas discusses the result and what we might expect from a Donald Trump Presidency.
